reviewText: The best secret rock band on earth. Once listened, always addicted. The best thing Kansas gave to the world. 1341 miles to get the Rockfeller, the opportunity to see again Oslo. Great DVD, Best band and wonderful rock music. Buy that one, as each one, closed eyes. Philippe & Katell France
What else can I say? The Rainmakers are truly pioneers and the creators of the soundtrack to most of my life.  If you have never heard them please check out this live performance - you'll be hooked.
